1. **Comment genuinely** on launches and forum threads. Pure value.
2. **Build reputation** as a leader who builds tools - {{role}} + open-source tools in your field credibility
3. **Natural opening appears** - someone asks about tools in your field or AI workflows -> share experience
4. **Never force it.** PH community respects authentic makers.

